Here &quot;a&quot; and &quot;D&quot; are integers and in the second case &quot;a&quot; is odd and &quot;D&quot; is congruent to 1 modulo 4.

The required conditions are &quot;α&quot; &gt; 1 and −1 &lt; &quot;α&quot;&#x27; &lt; 1.
These are satisfied in the first case exactly when &quot;a&quot; &gt; 0 and either formula_16 or formula_17, and are satisfied in the second case exactly when formula_18 and either formula_19 or formula_20.

