<doc id="519417" wikidata="Q1218511" url="?curid=519417" title="Bay Area (disambiguation)">
<text>Bay Area most commonly refers to the San Francisco Bay Area, the urban area surrounding the San Francisco Bay in Northern California.

Bay Area may also refer to:
*Guangdong–Hong Kong–Macao Greater Bay Area, an area around Guangdong, Macau and Hong Kong
*Monterey Bay Area, an area around Monterey Bay, California
*Tampa Bay area, an area around Tampa Bay, Florida
*Galveston Bay Area, an area around Galveston Bay, Texas
*Traverse Bay Area, an area around Grand Traverse Bay, Michigan</text><links>
